{"id":7843,"date":"2021-06-20T16:43:26","date_gmt":"2021-06-20T16:43:26","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/diegovz.com\/?p=7843"},"modified":"2023-08-03T14:53:03","modified_gmt":"2023-08-03T14:53:03","slug":"what-product-design-really-is","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/diegovz.com\/en\/blog\/what-product-design-really-is","title":{"rendered":"What Product Design really is"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-post\" data-elementor-id=\"7843\" class=\"elementor elementor-7843\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wavo-column-gap-default elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-a1532b4 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"a1532b4\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-311d2ef\" data-id=\"311d2ef\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3576184 elementor-widget elementor-widget-wavo-post-data\" data-id=\"3576184\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"wavo-post-data.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h1 class=\"post--data post--title post--id-7843\">What Product Design really is<\/h1>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-550fd37 wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"550fd37\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">June 20th, 2021 \/ Design management<\/p>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wavo-column-gap-default elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-2987fc48 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"2987fc48\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-1afed8b6\" data-id=\"1afed8b6\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wavo-column-gap-default elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-36d30361 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"36d30361\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-13b4fcdd\" data-id=\"13b4fcdd\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div data-split-settings=\"{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;chars&quot;,&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp2&quot;}\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ce1f068 wavo-headig-split heading-has-split-yes wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"ce1f068\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h1 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">We are the piece that connects users and business<span style=\"color:#DE5E91\">.<\/span><\/h1>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-54003dee wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"54003dee\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">In a product-based business environment, we have two main 'players' from our perspective as Product Designers :<br><br>\n\n\u25cf Users <img decoding=\"async\" draggable=\"false\" role=\"img\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\"\ud83d\ude42\" src=\"https:\/\/s.w.org\/images\/core\/emoji\/13.0.1\/svg\/1f642.svg\"><br>\n\u25cf Business <img decoding=\"async\" draggable=\"false\" role=\"img\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\"\ud83d\udcc8\" src=\"https:\/\/s.w.org\/images\/core\/emoji\/13.0.1\/svg\/1f4c8.svg\">\n\n<br><br>\nOn the one hand, our mission is to <b>empathize with our users<\/b> to understand their needs and frustrations. In this way we will be able to design interfaces, experiences and solutions fully adapted to them.\n<br><br>\nIt is very typical to find people who think that our work is based exclusively on that, that is, to design thinking only about the user, but if they have only explained that part to you... I'm afraid that <b>you've been told half the movie<\/b>.\n<br><br>\nHere comes the second part, and that is that our mission is also to help the company achieve its <b>business objectives and strategies<\/b>.\n<br><br>\n\nLet's look in detail at these two pieces that we need to put together, and why both are so important.<\/p>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wavo-column-gap-default elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-5787cff elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"5787cff\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-d1a329a\" data-id=\"d1a329a\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2554a88 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"2554a88\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div data-split-settings=\"{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;chars&quot;,&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp2&quot;}\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5348fcb wavo-headig-split heading-has-split-yes wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"5348fcb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Designing for users<span style=\"color:#DE5E91\">.<\/span><\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-17bd161 wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"17bd161\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">One of the <b>key pieces<\/b> in a product-based business environment are the <b>users<\/b>, this is clear.\n<br><br>\n\nWe can have a product with a great business model, but we need users to use it for the value to be real.\n<br><br>\nWhen designing for users, what we are doing is <b>building a customized product<\/b> for them. We achieve this by researching and empathizing to get a <b>deep understanding<\/b> of their goals, needs, frustrations, <a style=\"color:#5553a0; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https:\/\/diegovz.com\/en\/blog\/mental-models-in-ux\" target=\"_blank\">mental models<\/a>, etc.\n<br><br>\nA very common mistake is to think that we already know what our users need \"because we are users too\". This is totally incorrect for the following two reasons:  <\/p>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4fece1e elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"4fece1e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"wavo-column-gap-default elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-57a6625 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"57a6625\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-8d41a22\" data-id=\"8d41a22\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-da04fe0 wavo-stroke wavo-has-stroke-yes elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget-mobile__width-initial wavo-transform transform-type-translate wavo-has-stroke-type stroke-type-full elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"da04fe0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">01<\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-17ced28\" data-id=\"17ced28\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d9073e2 wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"d9073e2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h5 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">You know too much about the product<\/h5>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-299d43c wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"299d43c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">We are the ones who are designing the screens, the flows, the interactions.... In the end we know perfectly well how it all works, and that's cheating. \ud83d\ude09<\/p>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"wavo-column-gap-default elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-ef3ecf8 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"ef3ecf8\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-63e67f5\" data-id=\"63e67f5\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-51175fb wavo-stroke wavo-has-stroke-yes elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget-mobile__width-initial wavo-transform transform-type-translate wavo-has-stroke-type stroke-type-full elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"51175fb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">02<\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-bd8da11\" data-id=\"bd8da11\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b29b3cb wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"b29b3cb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h5 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">You are biased<\/h5>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-152e103 wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"152e103\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Confirmation bias, sunk cost bias, availability bias... We are subject to a multitude of biases. To avoid falling into them and to design correctly, we must follow the <a style=\"color:#5553a0; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https:\/\/xd.adobe.com\/ideas\/process\/user-research\/data-driven-design-for-user-experience\/\" target=\"_blank\">Data-Driven Design<\/a> methodology, which consists of making decisions based on data.<\/p>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-12ae533 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"12ae533\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wavo-column-gap-default elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-e930689 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"e930689\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-b231a7d\" data-id=\"b231a7d\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-273329e wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"273329e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">In the end the following happens, and that is that in all sectors there are several companies offering the same thing, that is, there is <b>strong competition<\/b> among them, and what will the user do? Choose the product that he perceives that <b>best has been designed for him<\/b>.<\/p>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8571e6b wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8571e6b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\"><i>\u2014 \"If users don't achieve their goals on our product, they will do so on another one.\"<\/i><\/p>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b64f8e7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"b64f8e7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"wp-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1139\" height=\"669\" src=\"https:\/\/diegovz.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/disenando_para_usuarioss.svg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-7806\" alt=\"\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption class=\"widget-image-caption wp-caption-text\">Designing for users<\/figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wavo-column-gap-default elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-efe9490 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"efe9490\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-bb7edbc\" data-id=\"bb7edbc\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-dd3d719 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"dd3d719\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div data-split-settings=\"{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;chars&quot;,&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp2&quot;}\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0e514f7 wavo-headig-split heading-has-split-yes wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"0e514f7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Designing for business<span style=\"color:#DE5E91\">.<\/span><\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d81cd69 wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"d81cd69\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Keep in mind that a Product Designer has to have a product mentality (as the name suggests), and therefore has to take into account the business objectives and strategies of the company.\n\n<br><br>\n\nIn the end we are working on a <b>product that must be profitable<\/b> in some way, so we cannot forget to help the company meet its objectives and goals.\n\n<br><br>\n\nFor the company, <b>users are of vital importance<\/b> for its growth, but so is making its product profitable and allowing it to stay in the market. Our job here is to help the product team improve different KPIs<b> <\/b>that are key to the <b>growth of companies<\/b>, such as:<\/p>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4beae19 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"4beae19\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"wavo-column-gap-default elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-000a555 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"000a555\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-81caba2\" data-id=\"81caba2\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1e1bb73 wavo-stroke wavo-has-stroke-yes elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget-mobile__width-initial wavo-transform transform-type-translate wavo-has-stroke-type stroke-type-full elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"1e1bb73\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">01<\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-20747d7\" data-id=\"20747d7\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-35e5221 wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"35e5221\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h5 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">GMV<\/h5>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-257bd26 wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"257bd26\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Total value of sales during a given period of time.<\/p>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"wavo-column-gap-default elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-7a346ed elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"7a346ed\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-ce2c35d\" data-id=\"ce2c35d\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0827637 wavo-stroke wavo-has-stroke-yes elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget-mobile__width-initial wavo-transform transform-type-translate wavo-has-stroke-type stroke-type-full elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"0827637\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">02<\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-4dd5b91\" data-id=\"4dd5b91\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-57bf402 wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"57bf402\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h5 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Add to cart<\/h5>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6f5dece wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"6f5dece\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Number of users who add a product to the shopping cart. <\/p>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"wavo-column-gap-default elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-149118f elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"149118f\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-2fe39a7\" data-id=\"2fe39a7\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c413abf wavo-stroke wavo-has-stroke-yes elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget-mobile__width-initial wavo-transform transform-type-translate wavo-has-stroke-type stroke-type-full elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"c413abf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">03<\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-6ca4990\" data-id=\"6ca4990\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b832302 wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"b832302\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h5 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Conversion<\/h5>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c27d5c2 wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"c27d5c2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Number of users who have completed a given goal.<\/p>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"wavo-column-gap-default elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-f3bcf5f elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"f3bcf5f\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-9dc794c\" data-id=\"9dc794c\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4ca9e27 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"4ca9e27\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8315a14 wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8315a14\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\"><i>\u2014 \"If a product is not profitable, it will probably end up disappearing.\"<\/i><\/p>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1ba4f35 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"1ba4f35\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"wp-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1139\" height=\"669\" src=\"https:\/\/diegovz.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/disenandos_para_negociooo.svg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-7807\" alt=\"\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption class=\"widget-image-caption wp-caption-text\">Designing for business<\/figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bd07952 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"bd07952\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wavo-column-gap-default elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-afdd1a5 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"afdd1a5\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-8a24682\" data-id=\"8a24682\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div data-split-settings=\"{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;chars&quot;,&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp2&quot;}\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-efa0d79 wavo-headig-split heading-has-split-yes wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"efa0d79\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Finding the perfect balance<span style=\"color:#DE5E91\">.<\/span><\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8bacb3d wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8bacb3d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">These two aforementioned 'players' are of great importance to the company, and it is here where the <b>difficulty<\/b> of our work as Product Designers lies, in <b>finding the perfect balance<\/b> between business requirements and user needs.\n<br><br>\nFrom time to time, it is quite typical to feel <b>pushed<\/b> due to excessive business requirements, and this usually results in a lousy user experience.\n<br><br>\nHow to solve this? <b>Sit down and talk to business and product.<\/b><\/p>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-756b288 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"756b288\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"wp-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"368\" height=\"378\" src=\"https:\/\/diegovz.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/balance_negocio_usuarios.svg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-7833\" alt=\"\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption class=\"widget-image-caption wp-caption-text\">Balance between business and users<\/figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b6a2920 wavo-transform transform-type-translate elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"b6a2920\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Here, our task is going to be to listen to them, understand them and finally show them all the knowledge obtained during our user research. <br><br>Yes, it's time to put the data on the table and.... Negotiate with them the <b>perfect balance<\/b>!  <img decoding=\"async\" draggable=\"false\" role=\"img\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\"\ud83e\udd18\" src=\"https:\/\/s.w.org\/images\/core\/emoji\/13.0.1\/svg\/1f918.svg\"><\/p>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wavo-column-gap-default elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-41ded4c3 elementor-section-content-middle elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"41ded4c3\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-background-overlay\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-a685340\" data-id=\"a685340\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-03f1d61 premium-title-icon-row-reverse premium-title-color elementor-widget elementor-widget-premium-addon-title\" data-id=\"03f1d61\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"premium-addon-title.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\n\t\t<div class=\"premium-title-container style7\">\n\t\t\t<h5 class=\"premium-title-header premium-title-style7\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"premium-title-style7-stripe-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"premium-title-style7-stripe\"><\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"premium-title-style7-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"premium-title-icon premium-lottie-animation\" data-lottie-url=\"https:\/\/assets9.lottiefiles.com\/packages\/lf20_r6191vsq.json\" data-lottie-loop=\"true\" data-lottie-reverse=\"\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"premium-title-text\" >\n\t\t\t\t\tDo you share? \t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/h5>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-4cb0877 elementor-hidden-phone\" data-id=\"4cb0877\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-d2de735\" data-id=\"d2de735\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-dc4cf54 elementor-widget elementor-widget-shortcode\" data-id=\"dc4cf54\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"shortcode.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-shortcode\">\n<div class=\"juiz_sps_links  juiz_sps_counters counters_total juiz_sps_displayed_nowhere\" data-post-id=\"7843\">\n<p class=\"screen-reader-text juiz_sps_maybe_hidden_text\">Share the post \"What Product Design really is\"<\/p>\n\n\t<ul class=\"juiz_sps_links_list\"><li style=\"display:none;\" class=\"juiz_sps_item juiz_sps_link_shareapi\"><button type=\"button\" data-api-link=\"https:\/\/diegovz.com\/en\/blog\/what-product-design-really-is\"  title=\"Share on your favorite apps\" class=\"juiz_sps_button\" data-nobs-